  <entry>
    <title>利用halo搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="/2023/06/04/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8halo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2023/06/04/%E5%88%A9%E7%94%A8halo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="准备"><a href="#准备" class="headerlink" title="准备"></a>准备</h2><p>当买好云服务器后，要想运行halo，必须在云服务器添加8090端口，否则无法打开网站</p><p>所谓安全组就是虚拟防火墙</p><p><img src="E:\ProgramData\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220407150445718.png" alt="image-20220407150445718"></p><blockquote><p>注：</p><p>​授权对象 源：0.0.0.0&#x2F;0是指所有的IPv4地址，就是把这台云服务器的8090端口授权给所有IP使用，其实这样是不太安全的，可以给IP或IP段使用</p></blockquote><h2 id="安装环境"><a href="#安装环境" class="headerlink" title="安装环境"></a>安装环境</h2><h3 id="jdk11"><a href="#jdk11" class="headerlink" title="jdk11"></a>jdk11</h3><h5 id="CentOS"><a href="#CentOS" class="headerlink" title="CentOS"></a>CentOS</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">sudo yum install java-11-openjdk -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用以上命令安装完成后，用<code>java -version</code>查看是否jdk11</p><h5 id="Ubuntu"><a href="#Ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Ubuntu"></a>Ubuntu</h5><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">sudo apt-get install openjdk-11-jre -y<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><ol><li>创建新用户（可选）</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">1.创建一个名为halo的新用户</span><br>useradd -m halo<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">2.给新用户赋予权限</span><br>usermod -aG wheel halo<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">3.为新用户设置密码</span><br>passwd halo<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">4.切换halo用户</span><br>su - halo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>创建<strong>运行包</strong>目录app（名字随意），并切换到此目录</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">mkdir ~/app &amp;&amp; cd ~/app<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>下载jar包</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">wget https://dl.halo.run/release/halo-1.5.1.jar -O halo.jar<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li>创建<strong>工作目录</strong></li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">mkdir ~/.halo &amp;&amp; cd ~/.halo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li>下载配置文件到工作目录</li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">wget https://dl.halo.run/config/application-template.yaml -O ./application.yaml <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="6"><li>运行Halo</li></ol><p>​若发现root下没有app目录，则使用<code>cd /home/halo/app</code>切换目录，再使用<code>java -jar halo.jar</code></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">cd ~/app &amp;&amp; java -jar halo.jar<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​当出现如下日志，则说明启动成功</p><p><img src="E:\ProgramData\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220407154143037.png" alt="image-20220407154143037"></p><ol start="7"><li>打开<code>http://ip地址:8090</code>即可看到安装引导界面</li></ol><img src="E:\ProgramData\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220407154713556.png" alt="image-20220407154713556" style="zoom:67%;" />]]></content>
    
    
    
